divs: Sighting DetailsI was plying frisbe with my cousins and i saw this circular object moving down showing me the full circle, and i thought of well its a plane or something and sometimes it would flash kindof like when the sun hits metal. So me and my cousin where looking for it and it was on the other side across from where it first was, and this time it was moving up and still showing all of the circe and repeditly flashed it had no shape of any aircraft and my cousin and me think it is possibly a UFO and i would like to share this experience with the rest of you.
Summary: A disk shaped object showing me the full circle.
